Assess the following code snippets. Which of these does NOT illustrate a scenario that could indicate an empty code block vulnerability, assuming that each snippet represents the complete implementation of the intended functionality?

A. if (user.isAuthenticated()) {} // Intentional no-op for authenticated users.
B. try { performCriticalOperation(); } catch (Exception e) {} // Catch block left empty.
